12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
14 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 204 of Title 75A, unless there
15 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
16 A. As used in this section:
17 1. “Account” means a digital profile on a social media platform
18 that is created by a user;
19 2. “Connected account” means an account on the social media
20 platform that is directly connected to:
21 a. the minor user’s account, or
22 b. an account that is directly connected to an account
23 directly connected to the minor’s account;
